            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Aquii Lee is a male writer and creative strategist serving as Managing Owner of A Lee Creations. 
                        He crafts cross-genre fiction that blends cinematic tension, global themes, and cultural legacy, 
                        spanning from urban crime fiction thrillers to deep biblical fiction.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        His work explores what people fight for, what they bury, and what they become—stories that challenge 
                        boundaries while entertaining readers worldwide. With a strategic approach to narrative development, 
                        each project is meticulously crafted to resonate across cultures.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
                        As a storyteller at the edge, Aquii's mission is to create fiction that doesn't just entertain, 
